{"type":null,"faqId":19354,"title":"为什么通话时，手机贴近耳部时屏幕会自动关闭，离开后仍然为黑屏？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:9pt;}\n.p3{margin-left:1.4409722in;margin-top:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:9pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>手机屏幕上方靠近听筒的位置内置有接近光传感器。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>在通话过程中，手机贴近耳部或有其他物体遮挡住上方的屏幕时，手机会自动关闭屏幕，离开遮挡物后屏幕会自动点亮方便您操作。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>若在通话过程中，手机离开耳部仍然为黑屏，请检查上方的屏幕是否被遮挡。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=64249\" style=\"width:0.5in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span>为了保证您的正常使用，请注意不要用手机套或其他物体遮挡听筒及其附近的屏幕。使用屏幕保护膜时，也请勿遮盖感应器部位，建议您购买本手机专用屏幕保护膜。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":137,"faqType":"通话与联系人","useful":0,"unUseful":1,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"2495","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Calls-contacts","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1422608224000,"seriesProductName":"G628-TL00","visitedTimes":63,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":1,"times":1,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":1.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}